'''凱倫·舒·彭斯'''（{{lang-en|Karen Sue Pence}}，{{bd|1957年|1月1日}}），婚前原姓'''柏藤'''（{{lang-en|Batten}}），是一位[[美国|美国]][[教師|教師]]及畫家。凱倫是第48任[[美国副总统|美国副总统]][[邁克·彭斯|邁克·彭斯]]的妻子，曾任[[美國副總統配偶|美國第二夫人]]及[[印第安納州|印第安納州]]第一夫人。在任美國第二夫人的後期，凱倫重啟其教職，在[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]]的一所私立學校中任藝術教師。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年生活 ===
凱倫於1957年1月1日<ref>{{cite web |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161129211507/http://greatagain.gov/meet-future-second-lady.html |archive-date=2016-11-29 |url=http://greatagain.gov/meet-future-second-lady.html |title=Meet the Future Second Lady |publisher=Trump for America |access-date=2017-01-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]]的{{link-en|麥康奈爾空軍基地|McConnell Air Force Base}}出生，<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/remarks-second-lady-karen-pence-military-spouses-fort-carson-colorado |title=Remarks by Second Lady Karen Pence to Military Spouses |work=白宮 |date=2018-09-13|access-date=08-11-2020 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115082741/https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/remarks-second-lady-karen-pence-military-spouses-fort-carson-colorado/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cosmopolitan.com/politics/news/a62233/karen-pence-facts/|title=7 Things to Know About Karen Pence, VP Mike Pence's Wife|date=2017-03-29|publisher=Cosmopolitan|accessdate=2020-11-08|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110090643/https://www.cosmopolitan.com/politics/news/a62233/karen-pence-facts/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.deathandtaxesmag.com/305457/karen-pence-secret-marriage-karen-whitaker-mike-pence-indiana/ |title=Karen Pence's secret first marriage |newspaper=Death and Taxes |department=Politics |first=David |last=Bixenspan |date=04-10-2016 |access-date=2016-12-13 |archive-date=2017-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171119000731/https://www.deathandtaxesmag.com/305457/karen-pence-secret-marriage-karen-whitaker-mike-pence-indiana/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>其母為莉蓮·彭斯（1931年－2004年），<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tributes.com/obituary/show/Lillian-R.-Barcio-89232475 |title=Lillian R. Barcio Obituary |publisher=Tributes, Inc. |website=tributes.com |access-date=2016-12-13 |archive-date=2018-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181228011615/http://www.tributes.com/obituary/show/Lillian-R.-Barcio-89232475 |dead-url=no }}</ref>父親為約翰·M·柏藤（1931年－1988年），曾於[[聯合航空|聯合航空]]任職。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/6856360/the_indianapolis_star/ |title=John Batten dies; ex-airline official |access-date=2016-12-13 |date=06-03-1988 |newspaper=The Indianapolis Star |department=newspapers.com |archive-date=2018-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181228011712/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/6856360/the_indianapolis_star/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，兩人於凱倫年幼時已離婚，莉蓮·彭斯於1968年與男子伯納德·巴西奧（Bernard Barcio）再婚。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2S5jDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT249&lpg=PT249&dq=bernard+barcio+karen+pence&source=bl&ots=1SpwdcL2ZG&sig=_pug0n-tKIDHiEHyN2nqi0GBc40&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjurrOr997cAhVFPK0KHUq0Dj8Q6AEwDHoECAMQAQ#v=onepage&q=divorce&f=false|title=Pence: The Path to Power|last=Neal|first=Andrea|date=01-08-2018|publisher=印第安納大學出版社|isbn=9781684350384|language=en}}</ref>凱倫於印第安納州首府[[印第安納波利斯|印第安納波利斯]]的社區{{link-en|寬波紋村 (印第安納波利斯)|Broad Ripple Village, Indianapolis|寬波紋村}}長大，並於{{link-en|主教查塔德高中|Bishop Chatard High School}}就讀，畢業時擔任[[畢業生代表|畢業生代表]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://alumni.bishopchatard.org/karen-pence/ |title=Karen (Batton) Pence, '75, Indiana's First Lady |publisher=主教查塔德高中 |access-date=2016-12-13 |date=2016-09-19|archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117142014/https://alumni.bishopchatard.org/karen-pence/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Parker />其後，她在[[巴特勒大學|巴特勒大學]]修讀教育、副修藝術，<ref name=indystar>{{cite news|last1=Rudavsky|first1=Shari|title=Karen Pence is right at home|url=http://www.indystar.com/story/life/2013/12/12/karen-pence-is-right-at-home/3997289/|access-date=2016-07-15|newspaper=[[印第安納波利斯星報|印第安納波利斯星報]]|date=2013-12-12|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813181741/https://www.indystar.com/story/life/2013/12/12/karen-pence-is-right-at-home/3997289/|dead-url=no}}</ref>並於該校獲[[初等教育|初等教育]][[理學士|理學士]]及[[理學碩士|理學碩士]]學位。<ref name=Maloney />

=== 教師生涯 ===
凱倫在獲得學位後，繼續於印第安納波利斯開展其教育生涯，在該市的John Strange小學、Acton小學、Fall Creek小學和Orchard學校任教職。<ref name=indystar/>在凱倫的首個孩子出生後，她開始學習繪畫[[水彩畫|水彩畫]]，並開啟她繪畫房子<ref name=indystar/>及歷史建築物畫像的生涯。<ref name=sprvl />她大約於每年完成35幅畫作，其中一些是受委託繪畫的，而另一些則是在當地的藝術博覽會上出售。<ref name=Maloney />

她在彭斯出任[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院]]議員的十二年間，在[[維珍尼亞州|維珍尼亞州]]春田的私立學校{{link-en|以馬內利基督教學校 (春田)|Immanuel Christian School (Springfield)|以馬內利基督教學校}}任職美術老師。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Eli Rosenberg|date=2019-01-15|title=The school that hired Karen Pence requires applicants to disavow gay marriage, trans identity|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/arts-entertainment/2019/01/16/school-that-hired-karen-pence-requires-applicants-disavow-gay-marriage-trans-identity/|accessdate=2019-09-30|quote=the second lady had taught at the school for 12 years previously when Mike Pence was a member of Congress.|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129054949/https://www.washingtonpost.com/arts-entertainment/2019/01/16/school-that-hired-karen-pence-requires-applicants-disavow-gay-marriage-trans-identity/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 印第安納州第一夫人 ===
2013年至2017年間，彭斯任職[[印第安納州|印第安納州]]州長一職。她在任州第一夫人翌年，於2014年印第安納州第一夫人慈善基金會。該會為一促進兒童、家庭和藝術的組織，亦提供助學金和獎學金予有需要的人士。<ref name=Maloney>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.cosmopolitan.com/politics/news/a62233/karen-pence-facts/ |title=Who Is Karen Pence? 7 Facts About VP Mike Pence's Wife. |magazine=[[柯夢波丹|柯夢波丹]] |date=2017-03-20|access-date=2017-06-23 |last=Maloney |first=Maggie |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110090643/https://www.cosmopolitan.com/politics/news/a62233/karen-pence-facts/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>凱倫在2015年開辦了一家名為「"'That's My Towel!' Charm"」的小公司，銷售一些可以附著在毛巾上的小金屬飾物，令用家在使用時更容易識別毛巾的主人。然則，這項業務在其丈夫邁成為副總統候選人後結束。<ref name=Maloney />

=== 美國第二夫人 ===
[[File:Karen_Pence_official_portrait_(cropped).jpg|upright]]
[[File:Mike_and_Karen_Pence_Gold_Star_Wives_06.jpg|thumb]]
凱倫於2017年至2021年担任[[美國第二夫人|美國第二夫人]]一職，接替離任的[[吉爾·拜登|吉爾·拜登]]。她僱用了克里斯蒂安·金·內文斯（Kristan King Nevins）為參謀長，內文斯曾在前第一夫人[[芭芭拉·布什|芭芭拉·布什]]的任期中擔任過相同職務。<ref name=Parker /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/02/07/politics/karen-pence-chief-of-staff-kristan-king-nevins/ |title=Second Lady Karen Pence hires chief of staff |first=Betsy |last=Klein |date=07-02-2017 |publisher=[[有線電視新聞網|CNN]] |department=政治 |access-date=2017-06-23 |archive-date=2019-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411222920/https://www.cnn.com/2017/02/07/politics/karen-pence-chief-of-staff-kristan-king-nevins/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>凱倫在任期間積極推廣[[藝術治療|藝術治療]]予大眾認識，她是在丈夫擔任眾議員期間，在華盛頓的醫院就診時首次接觸這種療法。<ref name=sprvl>{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2017/feb/17/vp-pences-wife-aims-to-raise-awareness-about-art-t/ |title=Karen Pence, the vice president’s wife, aims to raise awareness about art therapy |newspaper=[[華盛頓時報|華盛頓時報]] |agency=[[美聯社|美聯社]] |date=2017-02-17|access-date=2017-06-23 |first=Darlene |last=Superville |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111222418/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2017/feb/17/vp-pences-wife-aims-to-raise-awareness-about-art-t/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=kleinart />2017年10月，她在參觀[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]立大學校園時，重點介紹了該大學自1990年代起開展的藝術療法計劃。<ref name="orlandosentinel2ndladykaren">{{cite news|last1=Rohrer|first1=Gray|title=2nd Lady Karen Pence unveils art therapy initiative at FSU|url=http://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/politics/political-pulse/os-karen-pence-fsu-art-therapy-20171018-story.html|accessdate=2017-10-20|work=Orlando Sentinel|date=2017-10-18|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402113251/https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/politics/political-pulse/os-karen-pence-fsu-art-therapy-20171018-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年1月，凱倫返回以馬內利基督教學校任教，擔任兼職藝術老師。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Eli Rosenberg |title=The school that hired Karen Pence requires applicants to disavow gay marriage, trans identity |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/arts-entertainment/2019/01/16/school-that-hired-karen-pence-requires-applicants-disavow-gay-marriage-trans-identity/ |accessdate=30 September 2019 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] |date=2019-01-15|quote=the second lady had taught at the school for 12 years previously when Mike Pence was a member of Congress. |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129054949/https://www.washingtonpost.com/arts-entertainment/2019/01/16/school-that-hired-karen-pence-requires-applicants-disavow-gay-marriage-trans-identity/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在聲明中，凱倫指出她「很高興回到教室裡，做我喜歡做的事」，並指她曾經「錯過了任教藝術的機會」。

由於該校在之前曾因拒絕[[同性戀|同性戀]]學生申請而受到批評，並被指控為[[恐同|恐同]]機構，因該校其中一項政策是允許學校拒絕「性不道德，同性戀或雙性戀」的學生，規則亦適用於學生父母和僱員。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2019/01/15/second-lady-karen-pence-stepping-back-into-classroom/2584374002/|title=Second Lady Karen Pence is stepping back into the classroom at a school that bans gay students|publisher=USA Today|date=2019-01-15|access-date=2019-01-23|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113084526/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2019/01/15/second-lady-karen-pence-stepping-back-into-classroom/2584374002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>凱倫在發布她重返教職的消息數天後，遭受媒體及LGBT倡導組織的嚴厲批評。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/karen-pence-slammed-by-lgbt-activists-for-taking-job-at-school-that-bans-gay-teachers|title=Karen Pence slammed by LGBT activists for taking job at school that bans gay teachers|publisher=[[霍士新聞頻道|霍士新聞]]|date=2019-01-16|access-date=2019-01-23|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210193914/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/karen-pence-slammed-by-lgbt-activists-for-taking-job-at-school-that-bans-gay-teachers|dead-url=no}}</ref>而副總統彭斯則在之後為妻子的專業和決定辯護，指責該等人士批評宗教教育的行為。彭斯認為此事件只是反對者用作批評兩人的藉口，並指出主要新聞機構對基督教教育的批評令兩人感到冒犯，希望媒體停止相關行為。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bustle.com/p/how-mike-pence-defended-his-wife-karens-job-at-anti-lgbtq-school-will-baffle-you-15836309|title=How Mike Pence Defended His Wife Karen's Job At An Anti-LGBTQ School Will Baffle You|publisher=Bustle|date=2019-01-17|access-date=2019-01-23|archive-date=2019-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030135011/https://www.bustle.com/p/how-mike-pence-defended-his-wife-karens-job-at-anti-lgbtq-school-will-baffle-you-15836309|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]間，凱倫曾因疫情導致的停課而改為網上授課，其後在2020年8月底復課後，返回教室任教。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nypost.com/2020/08/21/karen-pence-will-return-to-classroom-to-teach-next-week/|title=Karen Pence will return to classroom to teach next week|publisher=[[紐約郵報|紐約郵報]]|date=2020-08-21|access-date=08-11-2020|last=Lia Eustachewich|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115153238/https://nypost.com/2020/08/21/karen-pence-will-return-to-classroom-to-teach-next-week/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fox5dc.com/news/second-lady-karen-pence-returning-to-northern-virginia-classroom-next-week-vice-president-pence-says|title=Second Lady Karen Pence returning to Northern Virginia classroom next week, Vice President Pence says|publisher=[[霍士新聞頻道|霍士新聞]]|date=2020-08-21|access-date=08-11-2020|last=Lindsay Watts|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115041009/https://www.fox5dc.com/news/second-lady-karen-pence-returning-to-northern-virginia-classroom-next-week-vice-president-pence-says|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]中，凱倫曾出席共和黨候選人的競選活動及擔任主講為兩人助選。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.daytondailynews.com/local/karen-pence-visit-delayed-in-tipp-city/3AASBDIWDRE5DC2HG3WOR7JEN4/|title=Second lady Karen Pence campaigns for Trump in Tipp City|publisher=Dayton Daily News|date=2020-10-23|access-date=08-11-2020|last1=Jen Balduf|last2=Cornelius Frolik|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103151831/https://www.daytondailynews.com/local/karen-pence-visit-delayed-in-tipp-city/3AASBDIWDRE5DC2HG3WOR7JEN4/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbc15.com/2020/10/26/second-lady-karen-pence-coming-to-waterloo/|title=Second lady Karen Pence coming to Waterloo|publisher=WMTV|date=2020-10-27|access-date=08-11-2020|last1=Nick Viviani|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101035351/https://www.nbc15.com/2020/10/26/second-lady-karen-pence-coming-to-waterloo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，[[當勞·特朗普|當勞·特朗普]]及彭斯最終在選舉中落敗，凱倫於2021年1月卸任第二夫人一職，職位由[[賀錦麗|賀錦麗]]的丈夫[[任德龙|任德龍]]接任，而任德龍則為美國的首位第二先生。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8925039/Kamala-Harris-hot-shot-lawyer-husband-Doug-Emhoff-Second-Gentleman.html/|title=The first ever second mister! Meet Mr Harris, Kamala's Jewish hot-shot lawyer husband Doug Emhoff who won her heart after texting her from Lakers game and proposed while ordering Thai food|publisher=[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]|date=07-11-2020|access-date=08-11-2020|last1=Andrew Court|last2=Maqrtin Gould|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126060228/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8925039/Kamala-Harris-hot-shot-lawyer-husband-Doug-Emhoff-Second-Gentleman.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 個人生活 ==
在高中時，凱倫結識了第一任丈夫約翰·史蒂文·惠特克（John Steven Whitaker），惠特克為一醫學生，<ref name=Parker />他們於1978年8月4日在[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]][[布魯斯德縣_(德克薩斯州)|布魯斯德郡]]結婚，然則最終離婚。<ref>{{cite web|title=Texas Marriages, 1966-2010|url=https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:VTYS-FZY|website=familysearch.org|accessdate=2017-05-05|archive-date=2021-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220192438/https://www.familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:VTYS-FZY}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ancestry.com/sharing/9363309?h=d3b27f |title=Indiana, Marriage Certificates, 1958–2005: Michael Richard Pence |website=ancestry.com |access-date=2016-12-13 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115041356/https://www.ancestry.com/sharing/9363309?h=d3b27f |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Parker>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/karen-pence-is-the-vice-presidents-prayer-warrior-gut-check-and-shield/2017/03/28/3d7a26ce-0a01-11e7-8884-96e6a6713f4b_story.html|title=Karen Pence is the vice president's 'prayer warrior,' gut check and shield|last=Parker|first=Ashley|date=2017-03-28|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|access-date=2017-03-28|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209162322/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/karen-pence-is-the-vice-presidents-prayer-warrior-gut-check-and-shield/2017/03/28/3d7a26ce-0a01-11e7-8884-96e6a6713f4b_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

凱倫與彭斯是在印第安納波利斯的教堂裏相識，兩人皆定期到該市的聖托馬斯·阿奎那斯教堂（St. Thomas Aquinas Church）參與活動，<ref name=indystar/><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/acts-of-faith/wp/2016/07/15/what-it-means-that-mike-pence-called-himself-an-evangelical-catholic/ |title=What it means that Mike Pence called himself an 'evangelical Catholic' |newspaper=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] |first=Michelle |last=Boorstein |date=2016-07-18|access-date=2016-12-13 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119045724/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/acts-of-faith/wp/2016/07/15/what-it-means-that-mike-pence-called-himself-an-evangelical-catholic/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>其後，兩人首次約會的地點為印第安納州博覽會，他們在會場裏溜冰。經過約九個月的戀愛後，<ref name=Chokshi>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/20/us/politics/who-is-karen-pence.html |title=Who Is Karen Pence? A Brief Introduction to the Second Lady |date=2017-01-20|access-date=2017-06-23 |first=Niraj |last=Chokshi |newspaper=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024011702/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/20/us/politics/who-is-karen-pence.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他們於1984年8月訂婚，<ref name=Chokshi />並於1985年6月8日結婚。<ref name=indystar/><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/6890339/the_columbus_herald/ |title=Pence-Whitaker [marriage announcement] |newspaper=The Columbus Herald |department=newspapers.com |access-date=2016-12-13 |date=1985-06-21|archive-date=2019-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024052217/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/6890339/the_columbus_herald/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="PotentialSecondLady">{{cite news|last1=Glum|first1=Julia|title=Who Is Karen Pence? Meet Mike Pence's Wife, Potential US Second Lady From Indiana|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/who-karen-pence-meet-mike-pences-wife-potential-us-second-lady-indiana-2391680|access-date=2016-07-15|newspaper=International Business Times|date=2016-07-14|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119230419/https://www.ibtimes.com/who-karen-pence-meet-mike-pences-wife-potential-us-second-lady-indiana-2391680|dead-url=no}}</ref>他們原為[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]徒，後來在1995年轉為[[福音派|福音派]][[基督教|基督教]]。<ref name=Parker />

兩人共育有三個孩子，長子邁克（在美國海軍陸戰隊服役）<ref name=kleinart>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/04/14/politics/karen-pence-art-therapy-asia-pacific/ |title=Karen Pence highlights art therapy with Asia-Pacific trip |publisher=[[有線電視新聞網|CNN]] |date=2017-04-14|first=Betsy |last=Klein |access-date=2017-06-23 |department=政治 |archive-date=2019-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411204754/https://www.cnn.com/2017/04/14/politics/karen-pence-art-therapy-asia-pacific/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，長女{{link-en|夏洛特·彭斯·本|Charlotte Pence Bond|夏洛特}}和次女奧黛麗。<ref name=indystar/><ref name=Maloney />凱倫大部分時間都在印第安納州生活，在丈夫就任眾議員期間曾舉家搬到[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]居住。<ref name=Maloney /><ref name=sprvl />此外，凱倫亦是一名訓練有素的飛行員。<ref name=indystar/><ref name=Maloney />

而凱倫亦以推動藝術療法而聞名。<ref name="StarkHealingArts">{{cite news|last1=Stark|first1=Liz|title=How Indiana First Lady Karen Pence Came to Champion the Healing Power of the Arts|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/indiana-lady-karen-pence-champion-healing-power-arts/story?id=41152258|access-date=2016-08-16|publisher=[[ABC新聞|ABC新聞]]|date=12-08-2016|archive-date=2018-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728191013/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/indiana-lady-karen-pence-champion-healing-power-arts/story?id=41152258|dead-url=no}}</ref>她為女兒夏洛特於2018年出版的兒童讀物《馬龍·邦多的副總統生活》繪畫水彩插圖，該書的收益捐贈予慈善機構，包括一項藝術療法計劃。<ref name=wpost>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/hes-bunny-of-the-united-states-and-now-hes-the-hero-of-a-childrens-book-too/2018/03/13/28c53e3e-2626-11e8-b79d-f3d931db7f68_story.html |title=He's Bunny of the United States. And now he's the hero of a children's book, too. |first=Roxanne |last=Roberts |newspaper=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] |date=2018-03-14|access-date=2018-03-19 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128151141/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/hes-bunny-of-the-united-states-and-now-hes-the-hero-of-a-childrens-book-too/2018/03/13/28c53e3e-2626-11e8-b79d-f3d931db7f68_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

